quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  68,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  68,1,"noon, qasam hai qalam ki aur uss cheez ki jisay likhnay walay likh rahay hain"
  68,2,tum apne rab ke fazl se majnu nahi ho
  68,3,aur yaqeenan tumahray liye aisa ajar hai jis ka silsila kabhi khatam honay wala nahi
  68,4,aur bay shak tum ikhlaq ke barray martabay par ho
  68,5,anqareeb tum bhi dekh lau ge aur woh bhi dekh len ge
  68,6,ke tum mein se kon junoon mein mubtala hai
  68,7,"tumhara rab unn logon ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo is ki raah se bhatkay hue hain, aur wohi un ko bhi achi terhan jaanta hai jo raah raast par hain"
  68,8,lehaza tum inn jhutlanay walon ke dabao mein hargiz nah aao
  68,9,yeh to chahtay hain ke kuch tum madahnat karo (dhelay parjaio_to yeh bhi madahnat karen
  68,10,hargiz nah dabo kisi aisay shakhs se jo bohat kasmain khanay wala be waqat aadmi hai
  68,11,"taanay deta hai, chughliyan khata phirta hai"
  68,12,"bhalai se rokta hai, zulm o zayad-ti mein hadd se guzar jaane wala hai, sakht bad aamaal hai, jfaa car hai"
  68,13,aur aَn sab ayob ke sath bad asal hai
  68,14,iss bana par ke woh bohat maal o aulaad rakhta hai
  68,15,jab hamari ayaat uss ko sunai jati hain to kehta hai yeh to aglay waqton ke afsaanay hain
  68,16,anqareeb hum is ki soond par daagh lagayen ge
  68,17,"hum ne inn ( ahal mecca ) ko usi terhan azmaish mein dala hai jis terhan aik baagh ke malikon ko azmaish mein dala tha, jab onhon ne qisam khayi ke subah saweray zaroor apne baagh ke phal torhin ge"
  68,18,aur woh koi istanna nahi kar rahay thay
  68,19,raat ko woh soye parre thay ke tumahray rab ki taraf se aik bulaa is baagh par phir gayi
  68,20,aur uss ka haal aisa ho gaya jaisay kati hui fasal ho
  68,21,subah unn logon ne aik dosray ko puraka
  68,22,ke agar phal tornay hain to saweray saweray apni khaiti ki taraf nikal chalo
  68,23,chunancha woh chal parre aur aapas mein chupkay chupkay kehte jatay thay
  68,24,ke aaj koi maskeen tumahray paas baagh mein nah anay paye
  68,25,woh kuch nah dainay ka faisla kiye hue subah saweray jaldi jaldi iss terhan wahan gay jaisay ke woh ( phal tornay par ) Qadir hain
  68,26,"magar jab baagh ko dekha to kehnay lagey"" hum rasta bhool gay hain"
  68,27,"nahi, balkay hum mahroom reh gay """
  68,28,"unn mein jo sab se behtar aadmi tha uss ne kaha"" mein ne tum se kaha nah tha ke tum tasbeeh kyun nahi karte? """
  68,29,"o hay pukaar utthay pak hai hamara rab, waqai hum gunah gaar thay"
  68,30,phir unn mein se har aik dosray ko malamat karne laga
  68,31,"aakhir ko unhon ne kaha"" afsos hamaray haal par, be shak hum sarkash ho gay thay"
  68,32,"baeed nahi ke hamara rab hamein badlay mein iss se behtar baagh ataa farmaiye, hum apne rab ki taraf rujoo karte hain """
  68,33,"aisa hota hai azaab aur akhirat ka azaab iss se bhi bara hai, kash yeh log iss ko jantay"
  68,34,yaqeenan khuda taras logon ke liye unn ke rab ke haan Nemat bhari jannaten hain
  68,35,kya hum farmaa bardaroon ka haal mujrimon ka sa kar den ?
  68,36,"tum logon ko kya ho gaya hai, tum kaisay hukum lagatay ho ?"
  68,37,kya tumahray paas koi kitaab hai jis mein tum yeh parhte ho
  68,38,ke tumahray liye zaroor wahan wohi kuch hai jo tum apne liye pasand karte ho ?
  68,39,ya phir kya tumahray liye roz qayamat taq hum par kuch ehad o Paiman saabit hain ke tumhe wohi kuch miley ga jis ka tum hukum lagao ?
  68,40,inn se pucho tum mein se kon iss ka zamin hai ?
  68,41,ya phir inn ke tehra-ay hue kuch shareek hain ( jinhon ne iss ka zimma liya ho )? yeh baat hai to layein apne sharikon ko agar yeh sachey hain
  68,42,jis roz sakht waqt aa parre ga aur logon ko sajda karne ke liye bulaya jaye ga to yeh log sajda nah kar saken ge
  68,43,"inn ki nigehain neechi hon gi, zillat inn par chhaa rahi hogi yeh jab sahih o salim thay uss waqt aِnhin sjday ke liye bulaya jata tha ( aur yeh inkaar karte thay )"
  68,44,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum iss kalaam ke jhutlanay walon ka maamla mujh par chore do hum aisay tareeqa se inn ko batadreej tabahi ki taraf le jayen ge ke inn ko khabar bhi nah hogi"
  68,45,"mein inn ki rassi daraaz kar raha hon, meri chaal barri zabardast hai"
  68,46,kya tum inn se koi ajar talab kar rahay ho ke yeh is chti ke boojh taley dabey ja rahay hon ?
  68,47,kya inn ke paas ghaib ka ilm hai jisay yeh likh rahay hon ?
  68,48,"pas apne rab ka faisla sadir honay taq sabr karo aur machhli walay ( Younis aleh islam ) ki terhan nah ho jao, jab uss ne puraka tha aur woh gham se bhara howa tha"
  68,49,agar is ke rab ki meharbani uss ke shaamil haal nah ho jati to woh mazmoom ho kar chtil maidan mein pheink diya jata
  68,50,aakhir kaar uss ke rab ne usay bargzida farma liya aur isay Saleh bundon mein shaamil kar diya
  68,51,"jab yeh kafir log kalaam nasiyaat ( quran ) suntay hain to tumhe aisi nazron se dekhte hain ke goya tumahray qadam ukhaar den ge, aur kehte hain yeh zaroor deewana hai"
  68,52,halaank yeh to saaray Jahan walon ke liye aik nasiyaat hai
